My question is, if one is assigned this position, will it be their responcibility to be available for every event?<br>
 Perhaps I missunderstood, please clarify.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Didanu Fallingleaf<br>
